oration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #0=
00000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> <a=
 href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31585391.284418/aHR0=
cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMTAtMjYvbXVzay1=
3aWxsLWJ1eS10d2l0dGVyLWF0LXRoZS1sYXN0LW1pbnV0ZT9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNTI0MjNfTU9ORV=
